Take charge of your household appliances like never before with QBELL Connect. Experience the future of home management, where comfort, security, and efficiency meet at your fingertips. Join the smart home revolution and start enjoying a more connected, convenient lifestyle today!

Here is a step-by-step guide
1. Download our "QBELL Connect" app in app market, then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in "QBELL Connect" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable "QBELL Connect" skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say "Search complete";
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.
Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.
Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.
Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.
Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.
Alexa, set the bedroom light to green.
